        "data": "{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-5\",\"max_tokens\":1000,\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Viet script YouTube 3-5 phut cho Tu Bep Phuong Nam - tu bep canh kinh cao cap TP.HCM. Gom: TIEU DE SEO, MO TA VIDEO, SCRIPT (Intro 30s + Noi dung chinh + Outro CTA). Viet tieng Viet co dau.\"}]}"
